Package: lasagna
Type: Package
Title: Multi-Layer Graph Analysis for Multi-Omics Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: BigOmics Analytics SA
Maintainer: Ivo Kwee <ivo.kwee@bigomics.com>
Description: LASAGNA (multi-layer graph analysis) builds multi-partite
    graphs from multi-omics data layers and solves for condition-specific
    subnetworks. Supports interactive 3D visualization with plotly,
    visNetwork, and grimon.
License: Dual Commercial and Non-Commercial
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Depends: R (>= 3.5)
Imports:
    igraph,
    plotly,
    visNetwork,
    grimon,
    gplots,
    matrixStats,
    stats,
    utils,
    methods,
    grDevices,
    graphics
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
